{"product_id": "12180", "page": 8, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2011-12-23", "text": "A solid sequel in a time of games where they were not always so. More varied weapons, better graphics in a near-future style. Multiplayer was good too if you could get TCP/IP mode to work (including deathmatch and other modes, even including cops which is great fun!), and the missions were much more impressive then the originals. Well worth a play for free.", "username": "Finaldeath", "products": 623, "early_access": false}
